data.description: BRAND new hot water tank has been installed and the seller has a  NEW stainless steel range that is ordered and will be installed! Welcome to this beautifully cared for home!  Walking in you will find the front room that boasts a bay window, bringing in tons of natural light.  Current owner is using as an office, but could be used as formal dining or 2nd living area.  2nd living area may not be needed, as the garage conversion has more than plenty of room for a group of friends or family of any size and is plenty cozy with corner pellet stove that also helps on annual heating costs.  Garage can also be easily converted back, as the garage doors are still in tact.  As you move down the hallway, you will find a HUGE dining area that includes an oversized buffet area with lots of shelving and plantation shutters.  The dining area opens to the galley style kitchen that has been updated with granite countertops, new backsplash, LED can lights and has plenty of cabinet storage.  Just off of the kitchen is the laundry area and 1/2 bath that has been fully remodeled with granite and plantation shutters.  Out the back door you will find a large covered porch with a new roof, a perfectly manicured lawn, and a workshop with separate storage, that has electrical already run to it.  On the 2nd level of the home is the large primary bedroom that includes a new built-in wardrobe system.  The primary bath has was fully renovated in August 23 to expand it's size and comfort.  The other 3 bedrooms that are upstairs are almost just as large as the primary, so no arguing over who gets what room!  The hall bathroom has also been fully renovated with a shower/tub combo and tile surround.  Other upgrades to the property include: New Roof and Gutters July 23, New Electrical panel Oct 22, Wood Laminate Floor Fall of 22, and New ceiling fans.
